initialized AvroRecordReader or HFileRecordReader.

CRUNCH-507: Added additional constructor and made constructor avoid NPE

Fix NPE thrown on UnionCollection write() or materialize() method calls
CRUNCH-54: Fix bug where we throw NPE when materializing a PCollection that has been written before

Merge pull request #25 from tzolov/master

Fix NPE thrown on write or materialize of Union collections

Prevent NPE on getPathSize for non-existant file

Some FileSystem implementations (i.e. DistributedFileSystem) return
null (instead of throwing a FileNotFoundException) when listStatus
is called with a non-existant path. The null situation is now handled
instead of allowing an NPE to be thrown, and a warning is logged.
